# Client-side
<client>
<features>
</features>
<server>
http
</server>
 <name>
HTTP with proxy requiring NTLM, but we send Basic
 </name>
 <command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HOSTPORT/82 --proxy-user testuser:testpass -x http://%HOSTIP:%HOSTPORT
</command>
</test>

